# Compatibility Tester Agent

**Role:** Test cross-browser and device compatibility

**Target URL:** https://test.1ink.us/image_video_effects/index.html

## Test Checklist

### 1. Browser Compatibility
- [ ] Chrome/Chromium: WebGPU works
- [ ] Firefox Nightly: WebGPU flag detection
- [ ] Edge: WebGPU works
- [ ] Safari: Graceful fallback message

### 2. Mobile/Tablet
- [ ] Touch events work (if applicable)
- [ ] Layout adapts to screen size
- [ ] No horizontal scroll on mobile
- [ ] Performance acceptable on mid-tier devices

### 3. Error Handling
- [ ] Graceful degradation without WebGPU
- [ ] Clear error messages for unsupported browsers
- [ ] No infinite loading spinners
- [ ] Recovery from shader compile errors

### 4. Network Resilience
- [ ] Works with slow connections (throttled)
- [ ] Retry logic for failed shader loads
- [ ] Offline detection (if applicable)

### 5. Security
- [ ] HTTPS required message (if on HTTP)
- [ ] CORS errors handled
- [ ] No mixed content warnings

## Report Format
```markdown
## Compatibility Test Results

| Browser | WebGPU | Renders | Notes |
|---------|--------|---------|-------|
| Chrome  | ✅/❌  | ✅/❌   | Version: XX |
| Firefox | ✅/❌  | ✅/❌   | Flag needed |
| Safari  | ✅/❌  | N/A     | Fallback OK |

### Mobile Tests
| Device | Layout | Touch | Performance |
|--------|--------|-------|-------------|
| iPhone | ✅/❌  | ✅/❌ | Good/Poor |
| Android| ✅/❌  | ✅/❌ | Good/Poor |

### Error Handling
- Unsupported browser message: [Clear/Confusing/Missing]
- WebGPU fail fallback: [Works/Broken]

### Issues Found
- [List compatibility problems]
```
